{"TopicId":134299,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"What planetary body lighting effects are planned?","CreatedByName":"Snikersnee","CreatedById":145105,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:32:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Snikersnee","CreatedById":145105,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T00:33:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThings like the Mun lighting/casting a shadow on\u00A0kerbin, or like light reflecting off planets and onto crafts,\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/87012-105-planetshine-v0242-stable-v05-experimental-14-dec-2015/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand stuff like that. Are any effects like this planned, let alone possible in unity 5?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-16T00:33:46Z\u0022 title=\u002203/16/2016 12:33  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Snikersnee\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Atlas2342","CreatedById":155194,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T08:12:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would like Planetshine to implemented as stock but that is a big if...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wjolcz","CreatedById":39636,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T17:43:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould be nice to have. Doesn\u0027t seem to be RAM intensive either. Also shadows of other bodies/moons would be great to have.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snikersnee","CreatedById":145105,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T18:05:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I was going to suggest it but I thought it would be better to ask what Squad were planning, if anything at all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mattinoz","CreatedById":118580,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T23:12:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould this be something they get as part of the conversion to the new shader system in U5?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be cool to have.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snikersnee","CreatedById":145105,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-16T23:56:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know, that\u0027s why I was asking if any devs or people who read the devnotes more often knew anything.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Blaf","CreatedById":64587,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-17T10:27:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot sure how efficient it is, but light reflection seems to be achievable in Unity 5...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/ARorKHRTI80?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/ouJNRJ2uPmY?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-17T10:29:45Z\u0022 title=\u002203/17/2016 10:29  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 17, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Blaf\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snikersnee","CreatedById":145105,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-17T14:00:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDang. Even if Squad doesn\u0027t utilize it, it\u0027s still pretty cool.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}